July 29, 2017 1:24 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Indus Capital Partners, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Indus Capital Partners, LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm provides its services to university endowments, foundations, and national government investment funds; affluent families; and funds of hedge funds. It manages hedge funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity and hedging markets across the globe. It primarily invests in Asian markets. Indus Capital Partners was founded in 2000 and is based in the New York City with additional offices in London, Tokyo and Hong Kong.


152 West 57th Street28th FloorNew York, NY 10019United StatesFounded in 2000



Phone: 212-909-2888

Fax: 212-909-2878

www.induscap.com







